        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://masseffect.wikia.com/wiki/Codex" target="_blank">Browse the Codex &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>ABOUT US</h2>
        <p>Find out more information about the entire team here at N7 Headquarters and the story behind the creation of N7 Consumer Reports.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="~/Home/About">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
